'''四季合唱團'''（The Four Seasons）是美國的一個活躍於1960年代至1970年代的合唱團，也被視為是[[披頭四樂團|披頭四樂團]]成名之前世界上最成功的樂團之一。1990年，四季合唱團進入了[[搖滾名人堂|搖滾名人堂]]<ref name="hall">[http://www.rockhall.com/inductees/the-four-seasons The Four Seasons] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rockhall.com/inductees/the-four-seasons |date=20131013162108 }}. [[Rock_and_Roll_Hall_of_Fame|Rock and Roll Hall of Fame]]: [http://www.rockhall.com/ Main Website] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rockhall.com/ |date=20070704201219 }}. Accessed June 9, 2009.</ref>。1999年，四季合唱團又被選入了聲樂團體名人堂<ref name="vocal">[http://www.vocalgroup.org/inductees/the_four_seasons.html The Four Seasons] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vocalgroup.org/inductees/the_four_seasons.html |date=20071024151227 }}. By Richie Unterberger. [[Vocal_Group_Hall_of_Fame|Vocal Group Hall of Fame]]: [http://www.vocalgroup.org/ Main Website] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vocalgroup.org/ |date=20160830042000 }}. Accessed June 9, 2009.</ref>。四季合唱團是史上作品最暢銷的音樂團體之一，唱片全球銷量超過一億張<ref name="stone">[http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/frankievallithefourseasons/biography Frankie Valli & The Four Seasons] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/frankievallithefourseasons/biography |date=20090814193656 }}. ''[[Rolling_Stone_Magazine|Rolling Stone Magazine]]''. Accessed April 19, 2013</ref>。

